1
00:01:27,719 --> 00:01:28,040
You

2
00:01:29,719 --> 00:01:30,280
Chen Gongxi

3
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:31,760
Play a round with me today.

4
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:33,079
No bets.

5
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:36,079
Let's see if you deserve the title of Mahjong God.

6
00:01:36,159 --> 00:01:36,719
If you win,

7
00:01:37,319 --> 00:01:39,920
